title: Led Zeppelin Live at Ahmet Tribute
description:
Led Zeppelin Live at the O2 Monday December 10th 2007

I was fortunate enough to be there on Monday and it was awesome so thought I&#039;d share this with everyone so at least you can experience it until the DVD comes out next year.  

I cant take the credit for the recording as i found this on a different torrent site 
but was in Flac format and had no track names.  

I have simply converted to MP3 and added track names.

I have also removed 2 of the tracks which were just of the crown cheering for an encore and didn&#039;t really see the purpose of them being there.
